### Modified Files

#### [MODIFY] [app.ts](file:///d:/dev/thegaminghub/wa-group-reminder/src/app.ts)

Add wiring for `NewsScheduler` — import singleton, start, stop on SIGINT/SIGTERM, call `setNewsWhatsappService`.

```diff
+import { newsScheduler } from "./sheduler/NewsScheduler.js";
+import { setWhatsappService as setNewsWhatsappService } from "./sheduler/NewsScheduler.js";

 await reminderScheduler.start();
 await taskScheduler.start();
+await newsScheduler.start();

 setReminderWhatsappService(whatsappService);
 setTaskWhatsappService(whatsappService);
+setNewsWhatsappService(whatsappService);

 process.on("SIGINT", async () => {
   reminderScheduler.stop();
   taskScheduler.stop();
+  newsScheduler.stop();
```

#### [MODIFY] [WhatsappService.ts](file:///d:/dev/thegaminghub/wa-group-reminder/src/service/WhatsappService.ts) *(command registration)*

Register `NewsCommand` alongside the other commands (wherever existing commands like [TaskDigestCommand](file:///d:/dev/thegaminghub/wa-group-reminder/src/commands/TaskDigestCommand.ts#5-20) are registered).

#### [MODIFY] [.env.example](file:///d:/dev/thegaminghub/wa-group-reminder/.env.example)

